quran[23]{c,v,t}:
  47,33,Enywe abasuubila muwulile Nyasaye nende Omurumwa ne mulanyasia ebikhole bienyu tawe
  47,34,Toto balia bakhaya mana nibekalila injila ya Nyasaye mana nibafwa nibali abakhayi Nyasaye shalibaleshela tawe
  47,35,"Mana mulatendeya mwenya omulembe tawe ne enywe nenywe balashila, Ne Nyasaye ali ninanyu, ne shalabeema omurungo kwebikhole bienyu tawe"
  47,36,"Toto obulamu bwokhushialo nomubayo nende okhukalilisia, ne ni musuubila mana mwaria Nyasaye alabahelesia omurungo kwenyu ne shalabareeba emiandu chienyu tawe"
  47,37,"Ne nabareba , mana abatilile, muleemana, ne alarusia obusuku bwenyu habulafu"
  47,38,"Enywe ano mulangungwa murusie khu injila ya Nyasaye, ne mwinywe balimwo bemananga, ne wimana yeyimanga omwene, Ne Nyasaye no muyinda nanyu muli abatakha, ne nimukhaya Nyasaye alarera Abandu bandi balali enywe, mana bakhaye okhuba shinga enywe"
  48,1,Toto efwe khwakhwikulila obushili bwa habulafu
  48,2,"Kho Nyasaye akhuleshele ebionoono bibio biawaranjilila nende biawamalilikha, ne akhwitsusilie tsimbabaasi tsitsie, ne akhulunjisie khu injila ingolofu"
  48,3,Ne akhuhabine obuhabini bwa amani
  48,4,"Niye weshia obuyeenzefu mumioyo chia basuubili kho anyoole okhubameeta obusuubili hekulu wobusuubili bwabu, ne omukaanda kwabalwani bo mwikulu nende bo khushialo ni kwa Nyasaye, ne Nyasaye niye Omumanyi po Owamachesi muno"
  48,5,"Khoyenjisie Abasuubili Abasatsa Nabakhasi mwikulu mumikunda chiburangamwo emialo, balimenyamwo thsinyanga tsiosi, mana abaleshele tsimbi tsiabu, ne okho imbeli waNyasaye nikho okhubura okhukhongo"
  48,6,"Ne abahelesie eshinyasio abeshikhabili, abasatsa nabakhasi, nende abatsokasinjia Nyasaye abasatsa nabakhasi abapariranga Nyasaye amaparo amabii, kuliboolela omukalukhano omubii, Ne Nyasaye yabasinyishila,\tmana\tnabatsuba, nenabarecheshela omulilo kwa Jahannam, ne ni amakalushilo amabii muno"
  48,7,Abalwani beliyie bo mwikulu nende bomushialo ni baNyasaye ne Nyasaye Niwamani Owamachesi muno
  48,8,"Toto efwe khwakhuruma obe Omuloli, Omusuubisia, Omwikanyilisi"
  48,9,"Kho musuubile Nyasaye nende Omurumwa wuwe, ne mumukhoonye, ne mumwe eshiribwa, ne mwitsomie Nyasaye itsuli nende ingolobe"
  48,10,"Toto balia bakhunganga omukhono toto bonganga Nyasaye omukhono. Omukhono kwa Nyasaye kuli hekulu wemikhono chiabu, ne ulia ufunakanga indakano, afunaka khulwo okhumisia omwoyo kukwe, ne ulia okhola kayalaka Nyasaye, alamuha umurungo omukhongo"
  48,11,"Ababeduwi (abamenyi bomumasokholio) batong’a inyuma balakhuboolela mbu :“Omwandu kwefu nende Abandu befu bakhutiyisiye, kho khusabile eshileshelo,” baboolanga netsinimi tsiabu akalali mumioyo chiabu, boola mbu: “ ni wina unyala okhumukhoonya imbeli wa Nyasaye ni yenya okhubaha eshinyasio nohomba niyenya okhubaha amalayi, ne Nyasaye amanyile muno kamukholanga"
  48,12,"halali mwapara mbu Omurumwa nende Abasuubili shibalakalushila Abandu babu tawe, mana nikabasangasia emioyo chienyu, mana ni mupara amaparo amabii, mana ninuba Abandu baasikha"
  48,13,"Ne ulasuubila Nyasaye nende Omurumwa wuwe, toto efwe khwarecheshela abakhayi omulilo omululu"
  48,14,"Obwami bwo mwikulu nende mushialo nibwa Nyasaye, aleshelanga wayenya ne asandia wa yenya, ne Nyasaye ni omunji wobulesheli omukoosia muno"
  48,15,"Ne abatonga inyuma baliboola mbu “ Nimutsia okhubukula omwandu kweliyie (ghanima) mukhuleshe khutsie ninanyu, benyanga okhukalukhania amakhuwa ka Nyasaye, boola shimulakhulondokhwo tawe, endio nilwa Nyasaye yamala okhuboola imbeli, kho balaboola mbu : “enywe mulineshikhalikhali ninafu,” halali shibali bamanya tawe halali hatiti"
  48,16,"Boolela batong’anga inyuma mubamenyi bomumasokholio “baduwi” mwitsa okhulangwa mulwane nende Abandu ba amani po, mulwane ninabo nohomba balonde amalako, ne nimuwulila mwaloonda Nyasaye alabarunga omurongo omulayi, ne nimukhaya shinga mwaranjilila okhukhaya, Nyasaye alabaha eshinyasio eshilulu"
  48,17,"Omuwofu shafunanibwa tawe, nohomba omulema, nohamba omulwale, ne uloonda ka Nyasaye nende Omurumwa wuwe Nyasaye alamwinjisia mwikulu mumikunda chibura hasi wachio emialo, ne ukhaya alamuhelesia eshinyasio eshilulu"